		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />We should definitely make our own Tape Deck interface. It's the future of whatever it is we are doing... They still make Cassette tapes right?<br /><br />Anyway I think you'd need an actual computer program to run to display your encoded video stream of data. To reduce the possibility of performance/frame rate issues. But in the end a serial cable of some kind is probably better.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
