	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />The beauty of the original idea is that it is plain simple - just use existing hardware, point the gun at TV. Tape interfaces aren't available on the stock consoles, so it is not interesting anymore, you could just add a SD, USB, Ethernet or whatever interface as well.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


	<hr width="85%" />

	<table width="85%" cellspacing="3" cellpadding="0" border="0" align="center">
