	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />Still acceptable for an extra level in Battle City or Lode Runner, though. In fact, the concept could be extended even further - a save feature through a VCR. To save data, a game plays the blinking sequence that could be recorded on a VCR, and to load, you playback the recording reading it with Zapper. Even more fun than a mile long password.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


